|---|-------|---------------|----------|--------|
| 1 | No body size limits | A05 Misconfiguration | 🔴 High | Missing |
| 2 | No security headers | A05 Misconfiguration | 🔴 High | Missing |
| 3 | No rate limiting | A04 Insecure Design | 🔴 High | Missing |
| 4 | No authentication | A01 Broken Access Control | 🟠 Medium | Missing |
| 5 | PII exposure | A02 Cryptographic Failures | 🟠 Medium | Missing |
| 6 | No CORS policy | A05 Misconfiguration | 🟠 Medium | Missing |
| 7 | Binds to 0.0.0.0 | A05 Misconfiguration | 🟠 Medium | Missing |
| 8 | No error handling | A05 Misconfiguration | 🟡 Low | Missing |
| 9 | Hardcoded config | A05 Misconfiguration | 🟡 Low | Missing |
| 10 | No request logging | A09 Logging Failures | 🟡 Low | Missing |
| 11 | Server fingerprinting | A05 Misconfiguration | 🟡 Low | Missing |

